OL,6,FSpeaking to ITV News, FDA general
OL,7,Fsecretary Dave Penman said: "Everyone
OL,8,Fknew that we were going through a
OL,9,Fperiod of shrinking the civil service
OL,10,Fand government had signaled that. But
OL,11,Fthe scale of the cuts and the pace of
OL,12,Fthe cuts I think will have taken
OL,13,Fpeople by surprise.
OL,15,F"We're talking about something that's
OL,16,Fclose to 10% of the entire salary bill
OL,17,Fof the civil service over the next
OL,18,Fthree to four years.
